<number box="[669,725,1967,1991]" pageId="1" pageNumber="130" value="1933.0">1933</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(original designation and monotypy). The gender of the genus group name was not determined by 
<bibRefCitation box="[559,837,2002,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="130" refString="Berland, L. (1935) Nouvelles araignees Marquisiennes. Bernice P. Bishop Museum Bulletin, 142, 31 - 63." type="journal article">
