<number box="[769,829,2002,2027]" pageId="1" pageNumber="130" value="1935.0">1935</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. It refers to Nuku Hiva, the largest of the Marquesas Islands in 
<collectingCountry box="[271,471,151,176]" name="French Polynesia" pageId="2" pageNumber="131">French Polynesia</collectingCountry>
. It is here arbitrarily considered feminine, similar to and consistent with many wolf spider genera ending with an ‘-a’.
</paragraph>
